outputs.output_descr: The main purpose of the project is to support the exhumation, identification and return of remains of missing persons in Cyprus by providing significant operational means to the CMP (EC-3).

project_descr: Support to the Committee on Missing Persons Project on Exhumation, Identification and Return of remains of missing persons in Cyprus, 2011-2012 (3rd EC grant)
project_title: Support to the Committee on Missing Persons (EC-3)
